    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s been a super reliable ride for me and has been really well-loved. Everything is running smoothly, and it looks great inside and out\u2014perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for the next person to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have!",
