    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted 2014 Porsche Cayman S featuring the naturally aspirated 3.4L flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering linear power through a 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission. This mid-engine platform utilizes a lightweight aluminum-steel composite chassis, offering exceptional torsional rigidity and a low polar moment of inertia for surgical turn-in. Recent service includes a comprehensive PDK fluid flush and inspection of the VarioCam Plus timing system. The braking system retains high-friction cross-drilled rotors and four-piston monobloc calipers with excellent bite. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals remain robust, and the active suspension management provides a perfect balance between track-ready damping and street compliance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
