    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a prime example of a well-cared-for luxury SUV that balances performance with everyday utility. The Nebula Gray Pearl exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chipping on the front fascia and a small superficial scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the Parchment leather cabin is clean and odor-free, featuring heated and ventilated front seats that remain firm and supportive, despite light natural creasing on the driver-side bolster. All technological features, including the 12.3-inch navigation display, blind-spot monitoring, and the premium audio system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine runs quietly and delivers smooth acceleration, backed by a comprehensive service record. Recent work includes a full synthetic oil change, a fresh cabin air filter, and a brake system inspection. The vehicle sits on Michelin Premier LTX tires with plenty of life left. This is a solid, honest vehicle perfect for anyone seeking luxury reliability without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This model has been maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring a refined driving experience and consistent mechanical integrity. It represents an exceptional balance of performance and value for the discerning driver who prioritizes quality and longevity. A thorough inspection confirms its robust condition and well-preserved aesthetic appeal.",
