    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, well-maintained, and still looks fantastic on the road! Whether you're just commuting to work or planning your next big road trip, this car is totally ready for its next adventure. I've taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a new home where it'll be just as appreciated. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
