      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to address common E46 floor pan fatigue, and the dual-VANOS system has been recently overhauled with upgraded seals for optimal cam timing. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this platform is renowned for. Maintenance records confirm recent rod bearing replacement and a fresh valve adjustment, ensuring this naturally aspirated icon is ready for the technical B-roads.",
